:Namespace Prepl
вҚқ Prepl: A programmable REPL server for Dyalog APL
вҚқ Inspired by Clojure's prepl
вҚқ
вҚқ Protocol (pure APLAN):
вҚқ   Input:  APL expression, newline-terminated
вҚқ   Output: APLAN namespace, newline-terminated:
вҚқ     (tag: 'ret' вӢ„ val: 1 2 3)         вҖ” return value
вҚқ     (tag: 'ret')                        вҖ” no displayable result (shy/void)
вҚқ     (tag: 'err' вӢ„ en: 11 вӢ„ message: 'DOMAIN ERROR' вӢ„ dm: (...))
вҚқ
вҚқ Usage:
вҚқ   2 вҺ•FIX 'file:///path/to/Prepl.apln'
вҚқ   Prepl.Start 4200          вҚқ blocking
вҚқ   Prepl.LoadConga            вҚқ pre-load on main thread (вҺ•CY needs thread 0)
вҚқ   tidвҶҗPrepl.Start&4200      вҚқ on new thread (& is an operator: f&arg)
вҚқ
вҚқ Loads Conga from workspace if needed.

    вҺ•IOвҶҗ1

    LDRCвҶҗвҚ¬           вҚқ Conga instance (set by LoadConga)
    _stopвҶҗ0          вҚқ Stop flag
    _bufвҶҗ''          вҚқ Receive buffer (v1: single connection)

    вҚқ в”Җв”Җ Server Lifecycle в”Җв”Җ

    вҲҮ LoadConga
    вҚқ Load and initialize Conga. Copies from ws if not already present.
      :If 9вү вҢҠ#.вҺ•NC'Conga'
          'Conga'#.вҺ•CY'conga'
      :EndIf
      LDRCвҶҗ#.Conga.Init'prepl'
    вҲҮ

    вҲҮ Start port;z
      _stopвҶҗ0
      _bufвҶҗ''
      :If вҚ¬вүЎLDRC вӢ„ LoadConga вӢ„ :EndIf   вҚқ Skip if pre-loaded by bootstrap
      :Trap 0 вӢ„ {}LDRC.Close'prepl' вӢ„ :EndTrap
      zвҶҗLDRC.Srv'prepl' '' port 'Raw' 4096
      :If 0вү вҠғz
          вҺ•вҶҗ'Prepl: failed to start on port ',вҚ•port
          :Return
      :EndIf
      вҺ•вҶҗ'Prepl listening on port ',вҚ•port
      Loop
    вҲҮ

    вҲҮ Stop
      _stopвҶҗ1
    вҲҮ

    вҲҮ Loop;wres;rc;obj;evt;data
      :While ~_stop
          wresвҶҗLDRC.Wait'prepl' 5000
          :If 0вү 1вҠғwres
              :If 100вүЎ1вҠғwres вӢ„ :Continue вӢ„ :EndIf   вҚқ Timeout (rc=100)
              вҺ•вҶҗ'Prepl: wait error ',вҚ•wres
              :Leave
          :EndIf
          (rc obj evt data)вҶҗ4вҶ‘wres
          :Trap 0
              :Select evt
              :Case 'Connect'
                  _bufвҶҗ''
              :Case 'Block'
                  obj HandleBlock data
              :Case 'BlockLast'
                  obj HandleBlock data
              :Case 'Closed'
                  _bufвҶҗ''
              :Case 'Error'
                  _bufвҶҗ''
              :EndSelect
          :Else
              вҺ•вҶҗ'Prepl event error:' вҺ•DMX.(EN Message)
          :EndTrap
      :EndWhile
      {}LDRC.Close'prepl'
      вҺ•вҶҗ'Prepl stopped'
    вҲҮ

    вҲҮ obj HandleBlock data;text;idx;expr;response;id
    вҚқ Buffer incoming data and process complete lines
      textвҶҗ'UTF-8'вҺ•UCS data
      _buf,вҶҗtext
      :While (вҺ•UCS 10)вҲҠ_buf
          idxвҶҗ_bufвҚівҺ•UCS 10
          exprвҶҗ(idx-1)вҶ‘_buf
          _bufвҶҗidxвҶ“_buf
          :If (0<вүўexpr)вҲ§(вҺ•UCS 13)=вҠғвҢҪexpr    вҚқ Strip CR from CRLF
              exprвҶҗВҜ1вҶ“expr
          :EndIf
          :If 0<вүўexpr
              idвҶҗExtractID expr
              responseвҶҗEval expr               вҚқ вҚқID: is a comment вҖ” вҚҺ ignores it
              :If 0<вүўid
                  responseвҶҗ'(id: ''',id,''' вӢ„ ',(1вҶ“response)
              :EndIf
              {}LDRC.Send obj('UTF-8'вҺ•UCS response,вҺ•UCS 10)
          :EndIf
      :EndWhile
    вҲҮ

    вҲҮ idвҶҗExtractID expr;pos
    вҚқ Extract optional ID from trailing comment: expr вҚқID:uuid
    вҚқ Returns '' if no вҚқID: found.
      idвҶҗ''
      posвҶҗ('вҚқID:'вҚ·expr)/вҚівүўexpr
      :If 0<вүўpos
          idвҶҗ((вҠғpos)+3)вҶ“expr
      :EndIf
    вҲҮ

    вҚқ в”Җв”Җ Evaluation в”Җв”Җ

    вҲҮ rвҶҗEval expr;вҺ•PW;вҺ•PP
      вҺ•PWвҶҗ32767 вӢ„ вҺ•PPвҶҗ17
      вҚқ Execute in # context. Result in #.вҚҷr (not local вҖ” Serialise
      вҚқ can't resolve namespace refs held in local variables).
      :Trap 0
          :With #
              вҚҷrвҶҗвҚҺexpr
          :EndWith
      :Else
          :If 6=вҺ•DMX.EN
              rвҶҗ'(tag: ''ret'')'
          :Else
              rвҶҗErrAPLAN вҺ•DMX
          :EndIf
          вҶ’CLEANUP
      :EndTrap
      вҚқ Serialize вҖ” namespace, APLAN, display form, or literal fallback
      :If 9.1=вҺ•NCвҠӮ'#.вҚҷr'                          вҚқ Namespace instance?
          :Trap 0
              rвҶҗ'(tag: ''ret'' вӢ„ val: ',(NsToAPLAN #.вҚҷr),')'
          :Else
              rвҶҗ'(tag: ''ret'')'
          :EndTrap
      :Else
          :Trap 0
              rвҶҗ'(tag: ''ret'' вӢ„ val: ',(ToAPLAN #.вҚҷr),')'
          :Else
              :Trap 0
                  rвҶҗ'(tag: ''ret'' вӢ„ val: ',(ToAPLANвҚ•#.вҚҷr),')'
              :Else
                  rвҶҗ'(tag: ''ret'')'
              :EndTrap
          :EndTrap
      :EndIf
     CLEANUP:
      :Trap 0 вӢ„ #.вҺ•EX'вҚҷr' вӢ„ :EndTrap
    вҲҮ

    вҲҮ rвҶҗErrAPLAN dmx
    вҚқ (tag: 'err' вӢ„ en: 11 вӢ„ message: 'DOMAIN ERROR' вӢ„ dm: (...))
      rвҶҗ'(tag: ''err'''
      r,вҶҗ' вӢ„ en: ',(вҚ•dmx.EN)
      r,вҶҗ' вӢ„ message: ',(ToAPLAN dmx.Message)
      r,вҶҗ' вӢ„ dm: ',(ToAPLAN dmx.DM)
      r,вҶҗ')'
    вҲҮ

    вҚқ в”Җв”Җ APLAN Serialization в”Җв”Җ
    вҚқ вҺ•SE.Dyalog.Array.Serialise вҶ’ lines, 62583вҢ¶ вҶ’ compact single-line.

    вҲҮ rвҶҗToAPLAN v
      rвҶҗ1(62583вҢ¶)вҺ•SE.Dyalog.Array.Serialise v
      rвҶҗ(rвү вҺ•UCS 13)/r                        вҚқ Strip CR вҖ” protocol is LF-delimited
    вҲҮ

    вҲҮ rвҶҗNsToAPLAN ns;names;n;v
    вҚқ Serialize a namespace instance as (key1: val1 вӢ„ key2: val2 вӢ„ ...)
      namesвҶҗ{(вҢҪвҲЁ\' 'вү вҢҪвҚө)/вҚө}ВЁвҶ“ns.вҺ•NL 2 3 4 9      вҚқ trimmed name list
      namesвҶҗ(0<вүўВЁnames)/names                       вҚқ drop empties
      :If 0=вүўnames
          rвҶҗ'()'
          :Return
      :EndIf
      rвҶҗ'('
      :For n :In names
          :If rвүў'('
              r,вҶҗ' вӢ„ '
          :EndIf
          :Trap 0
              vвҶҗToAPLAN nsвҚҺn
          :Else
              vвҶҗ'''<err:',вҺ•DMX.Message,'>'''
          :EndTrap
          r,вҶҗn,': ',v
      :EndFor
      r,вҶҗ')'
    вҲҮ

:EndNamespace
